{"analytics_identifier":"OT1210","base_path":"/government/organisations/preventing-sexual-violence-in-conflict-initiative","content_id":"e474d31e-d466-4221-acdd-d8d4833e6043","description":"The Preventing Sexual Violence in Conflict Initiative (PSVI) aims to raise awareness of the extent of sexual violence against women, men, girls and boys in situations of armed conflict and rally global action to end it. PSVI is part of the Foreign, Commonwealth & Development Office .","details":{"acronym":"PSVI","alternative_format_contact_email":"PSVI@fcdo.gov.uk","body":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Preventing Sexual Violence in Conflict Initiative (PSVI) aims to raise awareness of the extent of sexual violence against women, men, girls and boys in situations of armed conflict and rally global action to end it.</p>\n\n<p><abbr title=\"Preventing Sexual Violence in Conflict Initiative\">PSVI</abbr> is part of the <a class=\"brand__color\" href=\"/government/organisations/foreign-commonwealth-development-office\">Foreign, Commonwealth &amp; Development Office</a>.</p>\n</div>","brand":"foreign-commonwealth-development-office","foi_exempt":false,"logo":{"crest":"single-identity","formatted_title":"Preventing Sexual Violence in Conflict Initiative"},"ordered_corporate_information_pages":[],"ordered_featured_documents":[{"document_type":"Press release","href":"/government/news/the-duchess-of-edinburgh-becomes-first-royal-to-visit-ukraine-since-the-start-of-the-russian-invasion","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6632414469098ded31fca7df/s712_duchess-of-edinburgh-kyiv-apr-2024.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6632414402f02aa4f31e4123/s465_duchess-of-edinburgh-kyiv-apr-2024.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/66324144df4c0c63311e411e/duchess-of-edinburgh-kyiv-apr-2024.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2024-04-29T00:00:00.000+01:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Duchess of Edinburgh visited Ukraine to show her solidarity with men, women and children affected by the Russian invasion.</p>\n</div>","title":"The Duchess of Edinburgh becomes first Royal to visit Ukraine since the start of the Russian invasion"},{"document_type":"Press release","href":"/government/news/uk-invests-in-global-grassroot-efforts-to-tackle-gender-based-violence","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/656628de312f400013e5d539/s712_16_Days_of_Activism_Graphic.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/656628de75007400131ded8d/s465_16_Days_of_Activism_Graphic.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/656628de75007400131ded8c/16_Days_of_Activism_Graphic.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2023-11-28T00:00:00.000+00:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The UK marks 16 Days of Activism to End Gender Based Violence, renewing efforts to work with partners to prevent violence and empower women and girls worldwide.</p>\n</div>","title":"UK invests in global grassroot efforts to tackle gender-based violence"},{"document_type":"Document collection","href":"/government/collections/international-alliance-on-preventing-sexual-violence-in-conflict","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6564ee6b1524e6000da10197/s712_lord-ahmad-new-york-psvi-oct-2023.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6564ee6b1524e60011a1018a/s465_lord-ahmad-new-york-psvi-oct-2023.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/6564ee6b1524e60011a10189/lord-ahmad-new-york-psvi-oct-2023.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2026-03-13T11:42:50.000+00:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>The Alliance is a group of states, multilateral partners, civil society organisations and survivors that coordinates action on conflict-related sexual violence. </p>\n</div>","title":"International Alliance on Preventing Sexual Violence in Conflict"},{"document_type":"Press release","href":"/government/news/countries-agree-concrete-change-to-end-sexual-violence-in-conflict","image":{"alt_text":"","high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/63866fe3d3bf7f7ebb66df38/s712_cleverly-zelenska.jpg","medium_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/63866fe3d3bf7f7eb32a9f2f/s465_cleverly-zelenska.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/63866fe3d3bf7f7eb32a9f2e/cleverly-zelenska.jpg"},"public_updated_at":"2022-11-29T23:01:42.000+00:00","summary":"<div class=\"govspeak\"><p>More than 50 countries and the UN agreed urgent action to end sexual violence in conflict at the UK-hosted PSVI Conference this week.</p>\n</div>","title":"Countries agree concrete change to end sexual violence in conflict"}],"ordered_featured_links":[{"href":"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/international-protocol-on-the-documentation-and-investigation-of-sexual-violence-in-conflict-training-materials","title":"Training: using the International Protocol"},{"href":"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/psvi-library","title":"PSVI library of resources"},{"href":"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/psvi-partners","title":"PSVI partners"},{"href":"https://www.gov.uk/guidance/psvi-working-with-parliament","title":"Working with Parliament"},{"href":"https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/international-alliance-on-preventing-sexual-violence-in-conflict","title":"International Alliance on Preventing Sexual Violence in Conflict"}],"ordered_promotional_features":[],"organisation_featuring_priority":"news","organisation_govuk_status":{"status":"live","updated_at":null,"url":null},"organisation_political":false,"organisation_type":"sub_organisation","secondary_corporate_information_pages":"","social_media_links":[{"href":"https://twitter.com/end_svc?lang=en","service_type":"twitter","title":"End sexual violence in conflict"},{"href":"https://www.facebook.com/EndSexualViolenceInConflict/","service_type":"facebook","title":"End sexual violence in conflict"}]},"document_type":"organisation","first_published_at":"2017-01-20T16:51:51+00:00","links":{"available_translations":[{"analytics_identifier":"OT1210","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/preventing-sexual-violence-in-conflict-initiative","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/preventing-sexual-violence-in-conflict-initiative","base_path":"/government/organisations/preventing-sexual-violence-in-conflict-initiative","content_id":"e474d31e-d466-4221-acdd-d8d4833e6043","document_type":"organisation","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2023-10-27T16:38:59Z","schema_name":"organisation","title":"Preventing Sexual Violence in Conflict Initiative","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/preventing-sexual-violence-in-conflict-initiative","withdrawn":false}],"ordered_contacts":[{"content_id":"a6d8bef1-1bec-4745-beb9-2be8ef255b24","details":{"contact_form_links":null,"description":null,"email_addresses":null,"phone_numbers":null,"post_addresses":[{"iso2_country_code":"gb","locality":"London ","postal_code":"SW1A 2AH","street_address":"King Charles Street ","title":"Foreign, Commonwealth & Development Office","world_location":"United Kingdom"}],"title":"Preventing Sexual Violence in Conflict Initiative"},"document_type":"contact","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-04-16T15:55:10Z","schema_name":"contact","title":"Preventing Sexual Violence in Conflict Initiative","withdrawn":false}],"ordered_parent_organisations":[{"analytics_identifier":"D1315","api_path":"/api/content/government/organisations/foreign-commonwealth-development-office","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/organisations/foreign-commonwealth-development-office","base_path":"/government/organisations/foreign-commonwealth-development-office","content_id":"f9fcf3fe-2751-4dca-97ca-becaeceb4b26","details":{"acronym":"FCDO","brand":"foreign-commonwealth-development-office","default_news_image":{"high_resolution_url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/621e4de4e90e0710be0354d7/s960_fcdo-main-building.jpg","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/621e4de48fa8f5490aff83b4/s300_fcdo-main-building.jpg"},"logo":{"crest":"single-identity","formatted_title":"Foreign, Commonwealth<br/>&amp; Development Office"},"organisation_govuk_status":{"status":"live","updated_at":null,"url":null}},"document_type":"organisation","links":{},"locale":"en","schema_name":"organisation","title":"Foreign, Commonwealth & Development Office","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/foreign-commonwealth-development-office","withdrawn":false}],"ordered_roles":[{"content_id":"84754dd5-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"<p>The Prime Minister’s Special Representative (<abbr title=\"Prime Minister’s Special Representative\">PMSR</abbr>) for Preventing Sexual Violence in Conflict works with governments, the UN, civil society and others to:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>strengthen accountability and tackle impunity</li>\n  <li>provide greater support for survivors</li>\n  <li>ensure gender equality is fully integrated in all peace and security efforts</li>\n  <li>deliver a more effective multilateral response to crimes of sexual violence in conflict</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>The <abbr title=\"Prime Minister’s Special Representative\">PMSR</abbr> also promotes and implements the <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm201415/cmhansrd/cm140616/debtext/140616-0001.htm#14061619000002\">commitments of the June 2014 Global Summit</a>.</p>\n\n<p>In addition to continuing the international campaign to raise awareness, the <abbr title=\"Prime Minister’s Special Representative\">PMSR</abbr> chairs the cross-Whitehall ministerial committee which brings together the Foreign, Commonwealth &amp; Development Office, Ministry of Defence and Home Office. The committee looks at implementation of UK commitments as well as what additional support we can provide politically and practically to key partners in order to secure measurable progress. The <abbr title=\"Prime Minister’s Special Representative\">PMSR</abbr> also chairs the PSVI Steering Board with NGOs, academia and experts.</p>\n\n<p>The <abbr title=\"Prime Minister’s Special Representative\">PMSR</abbr> undertakes these activities on behalf of the Prime Minister, and reports to the Prime Minister.</p>\n\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"special_representative_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-11-18T13:50:19Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Prime Minister’s Special Representative for Preventing Sexual Violence in Conflict","withdrawn":false}],"ordered_special_representatives":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/people/lord-collins-of-highbury","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/people/lord-collins-of-highbury","base_path":"/government/people/lord-collins-of-highbury","content_id":"f902adbe-ed6a-453a-9095-5a135105c9aa","details":{"image":{"alt_text":"Lord Collins of Highbury","url":"https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/media/668eb1b1ab418ab055592357/s465_lord-collins.png"},"privy_counsellor":false},"document_type":"person","links":{"role_appointments":[{"content_id":"0c6c37be-9002-49cd-b0f3-a542056de8a7","details":{"current":false,"ended_on":"2025-09-07T00:00:00+01:00","person_appointment_order":4,"started_on":"2024-07-09T00:00:00+01:00"},"document_type":"role_appointment","links":{"role":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/ministers/parliamentary-under-secretary-of-state-minister-for-africa--2","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/ministers/parliamentary-under-secretary-of-state-minister-for-africa--2","base_path":"/government/ministers/parliamentary-under-secretary-of-state-minister-for-africa--2","content_id":"0949f209-afba-4314-a00c-62b43700875d","details":{"body":"<p>Responsibilities include:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>Africa</li>\n  <li>United Nations, Commonwealth and multilateral</li>\n  <li>democracy and human rights</li>\n  <li>Prime Minister’s Special Envoy for Preventing Sexual Violence in Conflict</li>\n</ul>\n","role_payment_type":null,"seniority":100,"whip_organisation":{}},"document_type":"ministerial_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-04-25T15:45:25Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Parliamentary Under Secretary of State (Africa)","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/ministers/parliamentary-under-secretary-of-state-minister-for-africa--2","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-09-08T08:17:21Z","schema_name":"role_appointment","title":"Lord Collins of Highbury - Parliamentary Under Secretary of State (Africa)","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"20be8b71-f7ae-47f5-bcb8-4fdf92d34d42","details":{"current":false,"ended_on":"2025-01-01T00:00:00+00:00","person_appointment_order":3,"started_on":"2024-07-09T00:00:00+01:00"},"document_type":"role_appointment","links":{"role":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/ministers/lord-in-waiting-government-whip--7","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/ministers/lord-in-waiting-government-whip--7","base_path":"/government/ministers/lord-in-waiting-government-whip--7","content_id":"dc229e28-1045-4e81-b414-478126269f0d","details":{"body":"\n","role_payment_type":null,"seniority":102,"whip_organisation":{"label":"Baronesses and Lords in Waiting","sort_order":5}},"document_type":"ministerial_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-07-09T17:54:24Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Lord in Waiting (Government Whip)","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/ministers/lord-in-waiting-government-whip--7","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2025-01-06T15:15:24Z","schema_name":"role_appointment","title":"Lord Collins of Highbury - Lord in Waiting (Government Whip)","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"e3b6eba3-45f0-416e-9895-0c8f88d97b81","details":{"current":true,"ended_on":null,"person_appointment_order":5,"started_on":"2024-11-15T00:00:00+00:00"},"document_type":"role_appointment","links":{"role":[{"content_id":"84754dd5-c0f1-11e4-8223-005056011aef","details":{"body":"<p>The Prime Minister’s Special Representative (<abbr title=\"Prime Minister’s Special Representative\">PMSR</abbr>) for Preventing Sexual Violence in Conflict works with governments, the UN, civil society and others to:</p>\n\n<ul>\n  <li>strengthen accountability and tackle impunity</li>\n  <li>provide greater support for survivors</li>\n  <li>ensure gender equality is fully integrated in all peace and security efforts</li>\n  <li>deliver a more effective multilateral response to crimes of sexual violence in conflict</li>\n</ul>\n\n<p>The <abbr title=\"Prime Minister’s Special Representative\">PMSR</abbr> also promotes and implements the <a rel=\"external\" href=\"http://www.publications.parliament.uk/pa/cm201415/cmhansrd/cm140616/debtext/140616-0001.htm#14061619000002\">commitments of the June 2014 Global Summit</a>.</p>\n\n<p>In addition to continuing the international campaign to raise awareness, the <abbr title=\"Prime Minister’s Special Representative\">PMSR</abbr> chairs the cross-Whitehall ministerial committee which brings together the Foreign, Commonwealth &amp; Development Office, Ministry of Defence and Home Office. The committee looks at implementation of UK commitments as well as what additional support we can provide politically and practically to key partners in order to secure measurable progress. The <abbr title=\"Prime Minister’s Special Representative\">PMSR</abbr> also chairs the PSVI Steering Board with NGOs, academia and experts.</p>\n\n<p>The <abbr title=\"Prime Minister’s Special Representative\">PMSR</abbr> undertakes these activities on behalf of the Prime Minister, and reports to the Prime Minister.</p>\n\n","role_payment_type":null},"document_type":"special_representative_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-11-18T13:50:19Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Prime Minister’s Special Representative for Preventing Sexual Violence in Conflict","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-11-15T16:39:53Z","schema_name":"role_appointment","title":"Lord Collins of Highbury - Prime Minister’s Special Representative for Preventing Sexual Violence in Conflict","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"c920d765-72bc-4856-9951-d99115e9e04e","details":{"current":true,"ended_on":null,"person_appointment_order":4,"started_on":"2024-10-08T00:00:00+01:00"},"document_type":"role_appointment","links":{"role":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/ministers/government-spokesperson-for-equalities--2","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/ministers/government-spokesperson-for-equalities--2","base_path":"/government/ministers/government-spokesperson-for-equalities--2","content_id":"f5718276-4aca-4ad8-8e7b-ac1985dbde25","details":{"body":"<p>Lords spokesperson on equalities.</p>\n","role_payment_type":null,"seniority":100,"whip_organisation":{}},"document_type":"ministerial_role","links":{},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-10-31T17:43:44Z","schema_name":"role","title":"Government spokesperson for Equalities","web_url":"https://www.gov.uk/government/ministers/government-spokesperson-for-equalities--2","withdrawn":false}]},"locale":"en","public_updated_at":"2024-10-08T19:17:50Z","schema_name":"role_appointment","title":"Lord Collins of Highbury - Government spokesperson for Equalities","withdrawn":false},{"content_id":"8f64b691-139f-4ebb-bad5-29e827d5d9fc","details":{"current":true,"ended_on":null,"person_appointment_order":2,"started_on":"2024-07-09T00:00:00+01:00"},"document_type":"role_appointment","links":{"role":[{"api_path":"/api/content/government/ministers/deputy-leader-of-the-house-of-lords--2","api_url":"https://www.gov.uk/api/content/government/ministers/deputy-leader-of-the-house-of-lords--2","base_path":"/government/ministers/deputy-leader-of-the-house-of-